author: Bitstar_coin
content: The wait is over, you can now check your Jupiter exchange eligibility here -----> https://airdrop.jup.ag/       Quick explainer on allocation criteria:- Welcome gift: 200 $JUP for all regardless of tier- OGBonus: 500 $JUP for at least $10 volume on Jup V1 or 10 transactions on Mer V1 before March'22- Volume: Volumes used have same-mint and stable-stable arbs removed. Bots are attributed 50% of their volume- Consistency: 1.2X your overall volume for non-bots who transacted at least 6 distinct months- 2023 Multiplier: 2X your 2023 volume for non-bots who transacted at least once before 2023.DCA &- Limit Order: 5X your DCA & Limit Order volumeWhich of the criteria above are you qualify for?What are your price prediction?
